{"tid":334750,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯Naushki汽車入蒙古","createTime":"2017-07-25T04:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T09:19:58.000Z","uid":40855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f497b6d99731389568f1f4fe5270ca76eee4546f","tid":334750,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:20:33.000Z","msg":"喺Irkutsk想直車去烏蘭巴托，但362係國際列車，兩日要成六千幾盧布，賣飛話要平就千七盧布買半票去邊境Naushki再坐汽車過關。我無諗就買咗，今晚九點車，聽朝十二點到，得七百盧布喺身，淆淆底，諗緊使唔使再撳錢。有無巴絲試過咁行，可唔可以分享下？<br />\n<br />\n跪地求教。"},{"pid":"58fd2bed82972b781ca756dea1b1bd7e057161a2","tid":334750,"uid":40855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15b17345e4685e76ee545a588986bb2f0f9e2cd","tid":334750,"uid":62937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d39265423013260b93a1e4b0aaffb0760239071","tid":334750,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"上咗火車，聽日就到邊境<br />\n前幾日滿洲里入俄羅斯成車水貨客，等足八粒鏡，今次會唔會一樣<br />\n難道我會成為連登第一人咁過境"},{"pid":"5e1230157c8a39be3bed3dce8930927b95267227","tid":334750,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/213610_695d1b819171dd3eb7c51d84c245ba80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F213610_695d1b819171dd3eb7c51d84c245ba80.jpg&h=ba09a571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n變直播post會唔會無咁快沉底"},{"pid":"9f5a63dc53f9c379ebb5f840c3387de234406471","tid":334750,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/214042_127a58e4368557a8996